                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/57931515/">U-N Riede</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-03-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">喜欢道德经但不喜欢那些写出来的所谓的智慧</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
