<section class="reviews mod book-content">
    <header>
        <a href="new_review" rel="nofollow" class="create-review redbutt rr" 
            data-isverify="False"
            data-verify-url="https://www.douban.com/accounts/phone/verify?redir=https://book.douban.com/subject/1190528/new_review">
            <span>我要写书评</span>
        </a>
        <h2>
            道德经的智慧的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 2 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="4186248">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/4186248/" class="title-link">让我失望的版本</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-4186248"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/45907643/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u45907643-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/45907643/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Kleinblume</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar10 main-title-rating" title="很差"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-10-27"
      class="main-meta">2010-10-27 16:15:05</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_4186248_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  其实从第一篇就觉得解释有点牵强了，越读到后面，发现自己和作者丹明子的分歧越大，直到《宠辱若惊》这一篇，反复看作者的注释还是没参透，于是上网查了一下，并且翻了易教授的《先秦诸子百家争鸣》，才发现不仅注释不对，竟然连原文都有讹误，真是失望。很少评价会给最差一档...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_4186248_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_4186248_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="2982670">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2982670/" class="title-link">所谓道可道，非常道</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2982670"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/32935494/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u32935494-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/32935494/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">桃金娘30</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-02-07"
      class="main-meta">2010-02-07 20:13:57</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2982670_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  当初决定买《道德经的智慧》这本书时，是因为之前读《道德经》，对一些古文的意思不能完全理解。于是买了这本有解读的，但是，不知道为什么，读起来反而失去了原本自我对道德经的一些感觉。似乎印证了这句话。有些“道”，如果可以说出口，反而失去韵味。或者也只是我个人性格...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2982670_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2982670_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










